features.text:
Crypto-Calendar is a collection of 366 unique NFTs. Each day of the year is represented by one NFT. 

NFT can design the day that they own and change it at any time. Upload tool on www.crypto-calendar.com  

Join our Discord or just place a bet for your favorite day on OpenSea:

In this gallery you find all 366 days of the year. Click on an image to find out if your favorite day is for sale on OpenSea.

Place an offer if it's not listed for sale.

_________

Basement: January 1st - June 30th

1st Floor:   July 1st - August 8th

Rooftop:     August 9th - December 31st
